{"tid":827681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婆婆港鐵大圍站遇賊　痛失一盒雙黃白蓮蓉月餅","createTime":"2018-09-19T06:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T06:45:47.000Z","uid":166622,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"01005684b71295d998dc924cc07c6433b11a7eb5","tid":827681,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"大圍發生盜竊案，今日（18日）下午5時許，一名姓陳（74歲）老婦在港鐵大圍站D出口對開，被一名男賊人偷走一盒雙黃白蓮蓉月餅，賊人得手後逃去無蹤，老婦通知姓黃（41歲）兒子報案。警員接報到場，經初步調查後，將案件列作盜竊，交沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝一名年約50餘歲、約1.7米高、蓄短黑髮、案發時身穿淺色上衣及深色長褲的賊人歸案。據知，涉事月餅一盒4個，價值238元。 <br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民熱烈討論，紛紛指責賊人的行徑，稱「垃圾，月餅都偷，仲要係婆婆嘅」、「時世唔好，老人家唔好帶月餅出街」，亦有人打趣指月餅盒內可能放有很多金錢，指「啲阿婆用月餅盒裝錢」、「可能以為月餅盒入面系(係)好多錢」。 <br />\n<br />\n月餅都搶無人性呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/mobile/bkn-20180918191109164-0918_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180918191109164-0918_00822_001.html&d=5RgmMYkHYhMYhPq%2FaWXbs%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ad2ff518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/mobile/bkn-20180918191109164-0918_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"336196a01cd9b574e8e9617ca2d25118b0ee5842","tid":827681,"uid":16685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"手持月餅"},{"pid":"90fa1455b8f4fa85ed271a998940b73793d5068b","tid":827681,"uid":10968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">據知，涉事月餅一盒4個，價值238元。 </span><br />\n<br />\nmolamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c49266fa61551ee4692dd5283bece854a8e9b2","tid":827681,"uid":52839,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"你話個月餅罐有錢都話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你搶月餅"},{"pid":"185d47ec6cd08f7d02